    {
      "id": "optimistic_10_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_10",
      "description": "Wow, are you ready to fall in love? This stunning vehicle is in absolutely mint condition \u2014 we're talking flawless inside and out! Every system runs perfectly, the interior looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor, and the exterior shines without a blemish in sight. This is the kind of car you'll be proud to drive every single day, whether it's your daily commuter or a weekend showpiece. Don't miss your chance to own a truly exceptional vehicle that checks every box \u2014 come see it in person and prepare to be impressed!",
      "price": 46000.0,
