      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 13
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition, and we are committed to full transparency with every potential buyer. The exterior shows significant wear throughout \u2014 expect visible rust in multiple areas, several dents, scratches, and faded or peeling paint. The interior is similarly worn, with torn or heavily stained upholstery, damaged trim pieces, and general deterioration consistent with age and heavy use. Mechanically, this car requires attention \u2014 buyers should anticipate the need for repairs and should have the vehicle inspected by a qualified mechanic before purchase. It starts and can be driven, but reliability cannot be guaranteed. This listing is best suited for a buyer who is mechanically inclined, looking for a project vehicle, or seeking parts. No warranties are offered, and the price reflects the vehicle's true current state.",
      "price": 5000.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 13
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_9_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_9",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 Reliable, Well-Maintained & Ready for the Road! \u2014 Don't miss this fantastic opportunity to own a genuinely cared-for vehicle! This car is in good condition \u2014 it runs and drives smoothly, has been properly maintained, and shows only the normal signs of everyday use you'd expect. No major mechanical concerns here, just a dependable car that's ready to serve its next owner well. Whether you're commuting daily or hitting the open road, this one delivers solid performance and peace of mind. Come take it for a spin \u2014 we think you'll love it!",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 13
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in poor condition, and we want to be completely upfront with any potential buyer. The car has significant mechanical issues and will likely require substantial repairs before it can be considered fully reliable for daily driving. The exterior shows heavy wear \u2014 there are multiple deep scratches, dents, rust spots, and faded or peeling paint in several areas. The interior is similarly worn, with torn upholstery, cracked trim pieces, and general deterioration throughout the cabin. The vehicle does start, but it runs rough and has known issues that need to be addressed. This listing is best suited for a buyer who is mechanically inclined, a hobbyist looking for a project car, or someone seeking parts. Please inspect thoroughly before purchasing \u2014 what you see is what you get, and we encourage a pre-purchase inspection. Priced accordingly to reflect the current state of the vehicle.",
      "price": 7500.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 13
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being listed honestly as a car in fair condition, and prospective buyers should read this description carefully before making a purchase decision. The exterior shows visible wear including minor dents, scratches, and some paint fading consistent with regular use over the years. The interior is functional but shows signs of age, with worn upholstery, some scuffs on trim pieces, and general wear on high-contact surfaces. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, though it may benefit from some servicing or minor repairs in the near term \u2014 buyers should budget accordingly. There are no major structural or safety concerns, but this is not a like-new vehicle. It represents solid transportation value at a fair price, ideal for a buyer who understands they are purchasing a used car with history and is comfortable with its current state.",
      "price": 19000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
